thing upon which one eats;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing upon which food is eaten:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) but said to be not so called except"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when food is upon it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 360:) arabicized [from the Persian]: (S, Msb:) the pl. (of pauc., of the first, S, Msb) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axowinapN","text_ar":"اَخْوِنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (of mult., S, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuwnN","text_ar":"خُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) said by IB to be the only instance of its kind except"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buwnN","text_ar":"بُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biwaAnN","text_ar":"بِوَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuwunN","text_ar":"خُوُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kutubN","text_ar":"كُتُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbN","text_ar":"كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuwunN","text_ar":"خُوُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not used: (S:) the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AxwAn","text_ar":"اخوان","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axaAwinu","text_ar":"اَخَاوِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axaAwiynu","text_ar":"اَخَاوِينُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA, from a trad.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","Mgh","Msb","K","ISk","IF","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n11772","headword_ar":"خَوَّانٌ","root":"xwn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAy^inN","text_ar":"خَايِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxaw~aAnu","text_ar":"الخَوَّانُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S:) because he is [very] treacherous. (JK.) And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fortune."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEuw*u","text_ar":"اَعُوذُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA@ll~`hi mina Alxaw~aAni","text_ar":"بِا@للّٰهِ مِنَ الخَوَّانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I seek protection by God"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the day of the exhaustion of provisions."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.)       -A2-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuw~aAnN","text_ar":"خُوَّانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [accord. to the CK, each is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this seems to be a mis take, (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahorN","text_ar":"شَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The month"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"latterly called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiyEN AlA^aw~ala","text_ar":"رَبِيعٌ الاَوَّلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axowinapN","text_ar":"اَخْوِنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) but ISd says, \"I know not how this is.\" (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n11773","headword_ar":"خُوَّانٌ","root":"xwn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next precedes."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}